original: Jungkvist, Karl Johan Ragnar, jur. kand., Skövde, f. 30/7/14 i Uppsala av lektor Sigfrid Emanuel J. o. Ester Lindberg. G. m. Sonja Julander. Barn: Karl f. 45. — Stud :ex. v. Skövde h. a. 1. 34, jur. kand. v. Upps. univ. 38. Tingstjg. v. Västerbergslags doms. i Ludvika 39-41, tf. stadsfogde i Skövde fr. 44, ombudsman i Skarab. 1. stads-hyp:fören. fr. 43. Deläg. i jur. kand. o. fil. dr. Sigfrid Jungkvists jur. byrå i Skövde fr. 42.
translated: Jungkvist, Karl Johan Ragnar, law graduate, Skövde, born on July 30th, 1914 in Uppsala to lecturer Sigfrid Emanuel J and Ester Lindberg. Married to Sonja Julander in an unknown year. Children: Karl, born in 1945. Studied at Skövde high school, graduated in 1934. Graduated with a law degree from Uppsala University in 1938. Worked as a court clerk at Västerbergslags district court in Ludvika from 1939-1941, then served as temporary city bailiff in Skövde from 1944. Employed as legal representative for Skaraborg 1st city credit association from 1943. Co-owner of law graduate and PhD Sigfrid Jungkvist's law firm in Skövde from 1942.
